  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5de9fd2d-0dbe-460b-9eb4-b61f5ed5605b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-af92716d-fc3b-484a-b8db-33b7ca470a06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dc3ff996-0d04-469e-811a-9e5684de8007\">안녕하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54053db2-b043-4853-8962-034716961753\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29bd7d9a-65b2-45da-852d-cbd73920981f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccc0b066-5bb8-4dd9-b78c-b4f966346eab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2e654b20-6bf1-4468-823e-38e1a4325e68\">7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞에 있는 이수한의원입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aead94b1-dc3b-4683-bc82-d169c932b803\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0d19e4f0-0b6c-42b6-b8cc-e446118d047d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84fe5c8f-9afb-487b-930b-d7570c3000e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3c73572b-2784-4357-92c3-8600c316238d\">저희 이수한의원에는 환자분들의 몸 상태를 좀 더 정확히 관찰하고 진단하기 위해서 23년도부터 포터블 초음파 영상 진단기기를 사용해왔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-16c56ea8-ab78-489e-bb60-cc49faaf100b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85923f63-2240-43bd-a475-4c4714ab9c77\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d687a0ed-5be3-498c-9dab-4d04b302ee6c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-30478e5e-ee44-4f34-b647-bd3260244721\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5de9fd2d-0dbe-460b-9eb4-b61f5ed5605b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e669eb31-5186-41d0-a571-b3e51d5fa5c9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e669eb31-5186-41d0-a571-b3e51d5fa5c9\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfNTIg/MDAxNzUwNjcyMDExMzE1.DV1EoCyiOQVqf6LgdPTK6P7gKSDbLwgjmN0xK6rBegYg.kfDjQ8hsSpf4QL4YNTXB3oL3hgU7MoCcu1UezQcdm_cg.JPEG/%EB%B8%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%EC%BA%94.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"720\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1280\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfNTIg/MDAxNzUwNjcyMDExMzE1.DV1EoCyiOQVqf6LgdPTK6P7gKSDbLwgjmN0xK6rBegYg.kfDjQ8hsSpf4QL4YNTXB3oL3hgU7MoCcu1UezQcdm_cg.JPEG/%EB%B8%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%EC%BA%94.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfNTIg/MDAxNzUwNjcyMDExMzE1.DV1EoCyiOQVqf6LgdPTK6P7gKSDbLwgjmN0xK6rBegYg.kfDjQ8hsSpf4QL4YNTXB3oL3hgU7MoCcu1UezQcdm_cg.JPEG/%EB%B8%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%EC%BA%94.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-e669eb31-5186-41d0-a571-b3e51d5fa5c9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4f809bea-7e7c-41bf-8345-f8790fb4d849\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a579645f-3fc8-45bf-b3ec-a4696943d328\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6b7593d-39eb-495c-ab17-720ef8f62194\">GE 사의 Vscan Air 라는 휴대용 초음파영상진단기기를 사용했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a07cf33a-95e0-4129-bff1-157c97949ca4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-89f44d24-7824-4df5-99b8-349be4ba69ab\">자그마한 초음파 진단기기임에도 들고다니는 휴대성이 뛰어나고 양질의 초음파 이미지를 보여주는 진단기죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0087a2d3-af3e-4cb9-a153-ceefef507814\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-60331cdc-46a5-4294-9b40-1e2a4482a585\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03d27e9a-2532-4342-b9d4-b5527c82bd61\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bbb5990e-7b09-4c2f-a3cf-f2bb6e7100d2\">관절 힘줄 인대 근육 등의 질환에 아주 유용하게 잘 활용해서 환자분들의 현 상태를 정확히 관찰하고 진단하게 되니 치료율도 눈에 띄게 높아졌서 저희도 환자분들도 만족도가 아주 높았습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fe22b83d-d6f3-447d-be9c-3a66731d2e7a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-097ea7f6-2db2-4ae0-b7ce-a0a1b546ef98\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5bb1309e-fd78-4dd5-a19c-7e5158bafe41\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f0bedac0-742c-4898-ae88-4ec311708343\">그런데, 사용하다 보니 좀 더 선명하게 관찰해서 진단의 정확도를 높이고 치료율을 더 높이고 싶은 욕심이 생겼습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7974e39f-75c1-4e90-aeac-f8b901b7cd06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-447668e8-375a-41bd-8797-7a46a88da0e4\">더불어 여성질환과 내과질환으로까지 영역을 넓혀야 한다는 요구가 생기더군요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-15bac016-69ea-486c-bb9d-30088a288154\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-36089704-88a0-4095-8f2e-2a3e034110ec\">(Vscan Air 는 복부 질환의 관찰, 진단보조에는 한계가 있어요) </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ac0822a-7884-436b-a756-c0a7eb9796ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e2de64ea-980c-4531-a167-a2a6984e9b46\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b9b5190-a242-45e1-8139-26c6233f8aab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a48e33f-6f03-4c8e-9e48-dc76a9cb89b3\">그래서 역시 GE 사의 대표 초음파진단기기인 LOGIQ P9 이라는 덩치가 큰 초음파영상진단기기를 도입했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4f809bea-7e7c-41bf-8345-f8790fb4d849\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2282d3e1-42e2-4c92-829f-75adabd3d105\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2282d3e1-42e2-4c92-829f-75adabd3d105\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfMTI1/MDAxNzUwNjcyNDI1NjEz.FKscmsFj3jGT4RgBCDr4AEMTqtJeeDZAEFMQU7P1zn0g.xghuFo1p1K0HbsGE9l5KYwox7L7ll4w-8rzJpd9hfZgg.JPEG/P9_3.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"720\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1280\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfMTI1/MDAxNzUwNjcyNDI1NjEz.FKscmsFj3jGT4RgBCDr4AEMTqtJeeDZAEFMQU7P1zn0g.xghuFo1p1K0HbsGE9l5KYwox7L7ll4w-8rzJpd9hfZgg.JPEG/P9_3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA2MjNfMTI1/MDAxNzUwNjcyNDI1NjEz.FKscmsFj3jGT4RgBCDr4AEMTqtJeeDZAEFMQU7P1zn0g.xghuFo1p1K0HbsGE9l5KYwox7L7ll4w-8rzJpd9hfZgg.JPEG/P9_3.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-2282d3e1-42e2-4c92-829f-75adabd3d105\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script